John J. Greisch

Age : 62Public asset : 17,258,095 USDLinked companies :  Hill-Rom Holdings, Inc. -  Idorsia Ltd 





Summary 



Mr. John J. Greisch is Chief Executive Officer at Advanced Respiratory, Inc., President at Aspen Surgical Products, Inc. and President at Hill-Rom, Inc.He is on the Board of Directors at Hill-Rom Holdings, Inc., Advanced Medical Technology Association, Ann & Robert H. Lurie Children's Hospital of Chicago, Children's Memorial Foundation, Idorsia Ltd. and Shedd Aquarium Society. Mr. Greisch was previously employed as Independent Non-Executive Director by Actelion Ltd., President-International & Vice President by Baxter International, Inc., President-International Operations by Baxter BioScience Corp., President & Chief Executive Officer by FleetPride, Inc., and President, Chief Financial Officer & Treasurer by Interlake Corp.He also served on the board at TomoTherapy, Inc.He received his undergraduate degree from Miami University and a graduate degree from Northwestern University.



